additional_media_info.title: The rise and fall of Forever 21
additional_media_info.description: Forever 21 made $4.4 billion in revenue and was one of the fastest-growing empires. Now, the retailer is preparing to file for bankruptcy after alienating customers and struggling with e-commerce.
